I play minecraft, tf2, and other popular games. i hate among us and love horses and cantaloupes. i love it when cantaloupes interrupt my twitch stream. i love my friend jabibi's voluptuous buttocks and my favorite food is couscous.  I am very funny and despise my audience as they are not. I LOVE sans undertale and i was banned from smplive. i have an addiction to ketchup. i love funny cats they are so silly..
